    "updated_at": "2016-07-14T03:00:40Z",
    "body": "@paulcbetts Our use case boils down to this:\n- `BrowserWindow` has tabs\n- The content of each tab is in a `webview`\n\nThe tab content may be expensive/slow to compute so we have to use a `webview`. If we were to use an `iframe`, a slow tab would make the entire app feel unresponsive.\n"
