    "created_at": "2016-07-14T08:16:28Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-14T08:16:28Z",
    "body": "I don't know how browserhtml works, but if you don't trust the page to use node integration, you shouldn't trust it to use webview neither. Regardless whether we allow using `preload` attribute, merely having `<webview>` tag is going to cause security problems, it basically allows people to read everything on system.\n"
  },
