    "updated_at": "2016-07-15T09:25:29Z",
    "body": "I just realised since you don't support nested webview (#1130) a lot of this discussion is not relevant for my scenario.  Only applies to BrowserWindow pointing directly to URL that you may not control content of.\n\nPerhaps the webview/security doc pages could be updated to be clearer around the scenarios for webview, what is and isn't supported, basically addressing any security holes apart from known lack of sandbox which I'm fine with.\n"
